Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:43.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遺失了開啟樂園的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:48.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受懲罰死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:52.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向著深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:57.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}無法忍受的荊棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:01.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}鬆開的鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:11.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追尋著永遠被埋葬的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:20.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}請不要看這殘破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:29.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牽絆 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:39.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}請不要來這裡 這你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:46.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下著絕望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:47.96,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}現在、完結
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:53.61,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般閃耀於汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:43.35,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:48.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:52.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:57.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:01.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:11.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.92,0:23:20.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:29.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:39.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:46.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:47.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.14,0:23:53.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:43.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月亮在輕輕低語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:48.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以誰也聽不到的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:52.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不斷滿漲的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:56.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}消失漸遠的記憶中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:02.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}星星在密密記述著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:06.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以誰也無法解讀的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:11.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}無限的語言的渦旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:16.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}千億本書由此誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:24.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我的天空無限廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}時間在飛速的鐫刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:34.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}毫無所知的虛無
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:38.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}匯聚的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:41.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:48.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:53.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}揚起晦澀難懂的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:59.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}至少將這聲音傳至天際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:04.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}太陽也終會升起吧
